    %p <b class="name">Barre Infusion</b> Quickly and safely reshapes the entire body in a fat burning fashion. This class is a low impact, 45 minute workout that features 25 minutes of muscle-shaping isometrics at the barre and 20 minutes of Pilates inspired core work.  This class targets all major muscle groups and improves posture. The results feature tighter legs and butt, sculpted arms, and a stronger core.

    %p <b class="name">Vinyasa Yoga</b> This flow class is all about connecting breath (pranayama) to movement (asana). Expect a mix of vigorous standing postures and balances with heart opening back bends and hip opening postures, ending with a deep relaxation. Through the practice you will focus your mind, challenge your body, and ease stress. Each class will be structured differently by our expert instructors, so you’ll never get bored. Basic yoga experience suggested. (We also have Beginner Vinyasa and Power Vinyasa - for the advanced as well)

    %p <b class="name">Power Yoga <span class="level">All Levels</span></b> This class is more rigorous than a normal yoga flow and will raise your vitality and physical power. Incorporating simple but challenging poses, core work, and focused breath, this practice will amplify your personal power on the mat. Focus your mind and body in new ways to create exciting change. Suggested for those with some previous yoga experience, but suitable for all levels.

    %p <b class="name">Yin Athletica</b> Yin Athletica is a deep restorative class with long passive stretching sequences which includes some prone and kneeling postures. Addressing the opening and release of the major joints: deep spinal twists, profound shoulder and hip openers, to access the deeper layer of tissue (fascia) done with long 3-5 minute holds. Following a yin class, your body can feel deeply relaxed and often the effects of the release can last long after, releasing deep seated tension and emotions. Come enjoy and discover as you unfold!  This class is for all levels for the ‘athlete’ in all of us!  (We also offer a Yin Yoga class for the non-athlete)

    %p <b class="name">Yoga Sculpt <span class="level">All Levels</span></b> This class is a combination of yoga inspired movements and free weights for increased muscle endurance, strength, stamina, and flexibility. Our Yoga Sculpt is a total body workout designed to tone or ‘sculpt’ every major muscle group. Free weights serve as your own personal adjuster as you move through sun salutations and other yoga postures, enabling extra length and depth in each pose. Strength training is great way to build lean muscle, which in return, will have greater long term impact on your metabolism, even while resting.

    %p <b class="name">Barefoot Bootcamp</b> This class infuses the heart-pumping qualities of  classical calisthenics, body-weight exercises, plyometrics and traditional yoga inspired sun salutations to strengthen and tone your entire body. If you want to achieve the fitness benefits of a bootcamp without all the screaming and yelling, enlist in Barefoot Bootcamp!

    %p <b class="name">Core Inferno <span class="level">All Levels</span></b> You will surely feel the burn in this heated core class. Using core strengthening techniques from Floor Pilates, yoga and Barre classes, you will heat up from the inside out. Combinations and exercises target deep muscles, toning and strengthening the abdomen. The room will also be heated to around 85 degrees.

    %p <b class="name">Body Tone <span class="level">All Levels</span></b> Work your deep muscles and tone those ‘hard to reach’ areas! Body Tone uses functional and bodyweight exercises in partnership with isometric and small movements to leave you feeling sculpted and ready to take on the day!

    %p.large.subheader <b class="alt">Interested In Private Yoga?</b>

    %p Lateral Fitness is now offering private yoga sessions with our top instructors!  Are you new to yoga and interested in starting the practice, but want to learn the basics before entering a group class?  An experienced student looking to deepen your practice?  Are you working around an injury or physical limitation? Let us tailor a yoga practice to your specific needs and schedule.  Book a 60-minute session at your convenience, and enjoy access to Lateral's premium mats and props, as well as our spa-like locker rooms and amenities.

